parameters:
\C[2]In addition to Konoha, several other magical
girls are lined up in the same way... Around them,
bandits are making a fuss as a gallery, their
bodies restrained and exposed in obscene poses.

Alright! The actors are all here! Tonight, the
greatest race begins! It's the Pregnancy Derby
starting nowwwww!!!!!!

The gallery erupted with excitement as one of the
bandits roared loudly. It felt like they had been
eagerly anticipating this day.
I must endure and get out of here...!

The hellish race for the magical girls is about to
begin... Will Konoha be able to endure until the
end...?

W-What on earth is this... Are all of us magical
girls pregnant?! What are they planning to do?

Alright, alright, settle down! I'm gonna explain
the rules, you know! These pitiful pregnant
magical girls have no idea what's going on, you
see! Bwahaha!

Listen up, all of you! You're all in the pre-
delivery stage! It wouldn't be strange if you gave
birth at any moment! So...!

We, who are here, are going to carry out the
Welcome Sex! And those who can endure giving birth
until the end... will be released from here!

The outrageous explanation from the bandit left
all the magical girls here in shock. He started
talking about a horrifying race using the girls
before giving birth.

Now, let's see who can endure until the end! Place
your bets, place your bets, place your bets! It's
getting exciting, whooo!

Uoooohhh!!!This is the best!!I bet 100,000 Lo on
the girl on the left!!

D-Don't joke around! What do you mean by Delivery
Derby?! What do you think giving birth is?!

Huh~? It would be troublesome if you
misunderstood~ This is your only hope, you know?
Why are you saying such strange things?

Do you understand that if you endure until the
end, I'll let you out of here? Or maybe, what, you
want to give birth and end your magical girl
career like this? Hm?

Alright, looks like you all understand! Well then,
let's get started! Is everyone ready?! Have you
finished placing your bets?!

(It's frustrating, but I have to somehow endure
this... If I give birth... it'll be over)

No... no...! Nooo... I'm scared! I don't want it
to hurt!

(I must say, my acting is quite impressive! Now,
let's do our best!)

A race that is like hell for magical girls is
about to begin... Will Konoha be able to endure
until the end?
